    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Pocket Legend》讲述了主角穿越到一个充满灵魂附着的传说武器的异世界的故事。玩家需要将拥有不同能力的传说物品合理地放置在背包中，通过击败各种阻挠玩家的敌人来推动故事发展。这是一款结合了“背包”系统的Roguelike卡牌构建游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129790/extras/ab72c809b556aa43a882c8fe2cb54c4e.poster.avif?t=1771985142\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129790/extras/ab72c809b556aa43a882c8fe2cb54c4e.webm?t=1771985142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129790/extras/ab72c809b556aa43a882c8fe2cb54c4e.mp4?t=1771985142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一款“背包”Roguelike卡牌构建游戏，每张卡牌的能力会因其在背包中的位置、周围环境和遗物而有所不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >例如：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >相邻格子越多空位，攻击敌人就越强力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >背包内的障碍物越多，攻击越强力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >背包整理得越好，角色越强大。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于每回合都会抽卡，本游戏与那些设置好背包后就只需观察的游戏不同，玩家需要每回合不断整理背包，寻找最佳的组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129790/extras/63910e47f1ad238a7df58db1e72993b0.avif?t=1771985142\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129790/extras_big/63910e47f1ad238a7df58db1e72993b0.avif?t=1771985142 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >卡牌主要分为五大类：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>武器</strong> - 对敌人造成伤害。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>防具</strong> - 提升玩家角色的防御力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>技能</strong> - 即时触发多种影响战斗的效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>附加</strong> - 只需放置在背包中即可持续产生效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>障碍</strong> - 主要由敌人生成，干扰玩家的操作。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过这五种卡牌的组合，产生最大化的协同效应是游戏的乐趣所在，也是玩家的目标。战斗获胜后，玩家可以获得背包碎片，扩展背包空间，并获得更多卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129790/extras/e8d3d4eddb26ce8cd49ad05b8d2bc3e2.avif?t=1771985142\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129790/extras_big/e8d3d4eddb26ce8cd49ad05b8d2bc3e2.avif?t=1771985142 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >背包作为资源消耗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Pocket Legend》中，玩家可以自由安排背包内的道具。背包本身就相当于资源系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >世界观介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129790/extras/ca9bf166b9d2d098f299d67ee152d983.avif?t=1771985142\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129790/extras_big/ca9bf166b9d2d098f299d67ee152d983.avif?t=1771985142 width=800 height=246 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129790/extras/0210112fcaa4d25a7923803fe20ff251.avif?t=1771985142\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129790/extras_big/0210112fcaa4d25a7923803fe20ff251.avif?t=1771985142 width=800 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Pocket Legend》中，许多传说中的武器将会登场。  <br>例如：格拉姆、弗里德文、盖·伯格、阿隆戴特、雷瓦汀、提尔锋、菲尔诺特等，这些富有魅力的传说工具都附着灵魂，与玩家产生共鸣，陪伴玩家一起冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家通过次元穿越到“卢门西亚”这个世界，并获得“背包”的能力，因而卷入了巨大的事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129790/extras/ea48c67c8d1439b5cd360795138e24ea.avif?t=1771985142\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129790/extras_big/ea48c67c8d1439b5cd360795138e24ea.avif?t=1771985142 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角能否击败强大的敌人“塔涅布拉”，并回到原来的世界？请通过游戏来一探究竟吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家QQ交流群：929740575</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
